
  "[ Patient Input ]
       ↓
[ Symptom Analysis ]
→ Uses NLP or keyword matching to extract symptoms
       ↓
[ Illness Prediction ]
→ Maps symptoms to likely conditions using rule-based logic or ML
       ↓
[ Doctor Referral ]
→ Recommends the correct specialist (GP, cardiologist, etc.)
       ↓
[ Room Guidance ]
→ Directs patient to the appropriate department or room


